OL,7,FOne of the first investigations
OL,8,Fcarried out by a new body tasked with
OL,9,Fprobing outstanding cases from the
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland Troubles will be into
OL,11,FGuildford attack.
OL,13,FThe Independent Commission for
OL,14,FReconciliation and Information
OL,15,FRecovery (ICRIR) will examine the
OL,16,Fatrocity at the Horse and Groom and a
OL,17,Fbomb that detonated 30 minutes later
OL,18,Fat the Seven Stars pub in the city.
